WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:900000,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:00:08.091 --> 00:00:10.677 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Hah! Ohh...

00:00:10.760 --> 00:00:12.262 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Peace!

00:00:12.345 --> 00:00:15.098 position:50% align:center
All right! I finally managed to
turn into a decent-looking bat.

00:00:15.181 --> 00:00:17.225 position:50% align:center
I've gotta show
John and Ronaldo--

00:00:17.308 --> 00:00:20.687 position:50% align:center
Huh. Oh, yeah, I forgot that
they went shopping together.

00:00:20.770 --> 00:00:23.064 position:50% align:center
Hey, John, I'm treating
you to donuts today!

00:00:23.148 --> 00:00:24.441 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaks]

00:00:24.524 --> 00:00:27.110 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] I guess I'll
have to go find them, then.

00:00:28.611 --> 00:00:30.030 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Peace, peace, peace, peace.

00:00:30.113 --> 00:00:31.573 position:50% align:center
Peace, peace, peace, peace.
Peace, peace, peace, peace.

00:00:31.656 --> 00:00:34.075 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC grunting]

00:00:34.159 --> 00:00:38.747 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC sighs]
I'm beat.

00:00:38.830 --> 00:00:44.711 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] P-Peace, peace, peace,
peace, peace, peace, peace.

00:00:44.794 --> 00:00:47.130 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] All right! I can
open the window, at least.

00:00:47.213 --> 00:00:50.050 position:50% align:center
In this form, even everyday
movements are hard.

00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:51.259 position:50% align:center
Oh, well.

00:00:51.343 --> 00:00:54.220 position:50% align:center
To the outside world! Let's go!

00:00:54.304 --> 00:00:55.263 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC gasps]

00:00:55.347 --> 00:00:59.684 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC screams]

00:02:32.152 --> 00:02:34.070 position:50% align:center
--[PIGEONS cooing]
--[DRALUC grunting]

00:02:34.154 --> 00:02:36.031 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:02:36.114 --> 00:02:39.034 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] My adventure's about
to be cut short too soon!

00:02:39.117 --> 00:02:42.412 position:50% align:center
Whoa. What's up
with all these pigeons?

00:02:45.540 --> 00:02:48.084 position:50% align:center
Are you all right? Were you
attacked by those mean birds?

00:02:48.168 --> 00:02:51.338 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
You saved me, Hinaichi--

00:02:51.421 --> 00:02:55.717 position:50% align:center
You are the cutest! Oh, my
goodness, you're just precious!

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:57.052 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Peace.

00:02:57.135 --> 00:02:59.012 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI] You're so calm.
Are you used to people?

00:02:59.095 --> 00:03:01.431 position:50% align:center
My heart! I want to
love you and cuddle you

00:03:01.514 --> 00:03:04.559 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Wait, does she
really not recognize me?

00:03:04.642 --> 00:03:06.853 position:50% align:center
Could this be?

00:03:06.936 --> 00:03:08.688 position:50% align:center
Here, it's time to eat.

00:03:08.772 --> 00:03:10.565 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Could this
be my big chance to have

00:03:10.648 --> 00:03:14.694 position:50% align:center
Hinaichi fawn over me and
also maybe give me some blood?

00:03:14.778 --> 00:03:15.820 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI]
You're coming with me.

00:03:15.904 --> 00:03:17.530 position:50% align:center
You can ride in here for a bit.

00:03:17.614 --> 00:03:19.449 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Peace?

00:03:19.532 --> 00:03:21.034 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
My...

00:03:21.117 --> 00:03:24.245 position:50% align:center
How forward of you to put me so
close to your breast, Hinaichi!

00:03:24.329 --> 00:03:25.872 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC grunts]

00:03:25.955 --> 00:03:27.749 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] All this
jostling when she walks!

00:03:27.832 --> 00:03:30.377 position:50% align:center
I must brace myself,
lest I slide down!

00:03:30.460 --> 00:03:32.754 position:50% align:center
I shouldn't go too deep
into a girl's clothes!

00:03:32.837 --> 00:03:35.507 position:50% align:center
I am a gentleman.

00:03:35.590 --> 00:03:37.300 position:50% align:center
We're almost there.

00:03:37.384 --> 00:03:40.804 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Oh, I wonder what
Hinaichi's house might be like.

00:03:40.887 --> 00:03:43.932 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC screams]

00:03:44.015 --> 00:03:45.266 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI] I should have Handa
check to see

00:03:45.350 --> 00:03:47.310 position:50% align:center
if it's a vampire, just in case.

00:03:47.394 --> 00:03:48.728 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
No, please.

00:03:48.812 --> 00:03:51.356 position:50% align:center
Why must you insist upon doing
your job properly now?

00:03:51.439 --> 00:03:53.608 position:50% align:center
Where's the cookie-obsessed
freak I know and love?

00:03:53.692 --> 00:03:55.610 position:50% align:center
I want her!

00:03:55.694 --> 00:03:57.487 position:50% align:center
Look at the position we're in!

00:03:57.570 --> 00:04:00.949 position:50% align:center
If my identity is revealed now,
she'll never talk to me again!

00:04:01.032 --> 00:04:03.785 position:50% align:center
Or rather, she'll kill me, and
I'll never speak again, period!

00:04:03.868 --> 00:04:06.287 position:50% align:center
Come on, don't struggle.
Handa needs to--

00:04:06.371 --> 00:04:07.205 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:04:07.288 --> 00:04:09.082 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
Oh. Hello, Vice-Captain!

00:04:09.165 --> 00:04:10.583 position:50% align:center
Did you get a new pet?

00:04:10.667 --> 00:04:11.960 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC snorts]

00:04:12.043 --> 00:04:13.795 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
Sorry to bear bad news,

00:04:13.878 --> 00:04:15.922 position:50% align:center
but that impostor
is not a normal bat!

00:04:16.006 --> 00:04:17.549 position:50% align:center
Huh? [yelps]

00:04:17.632 --> 00:04:18.299 position:50% align:center
This guy is--

00:04:18.383 --> 00:04:19.634 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Peace!

00:04:19.718 --> 00:04:21.011 position:50% align:center
Uh?

00:04:21.094 --> 00:04:23.304 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Wait, Handa.
It's me! Draluc! I got lost!

00:04:23.388 --> 00:04:26.182 position:50% align:center
I can't let Hinaichi find out!
Please gloss over this somehow!

00:04:26.266 --> 00:04:27.851 position:50% align:center
You've got to help me!

00:04:27.934 --> 00:04:30.812 position:50% align:center
Okay, so if it's not
a normal bat, then what is it?

00:04:30.895 --> 00:04:33.732 position:50% align:center
What's up, guys?

00:04:33.815 --> 00:04:35.233 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
It's, uh...

00:04:35.316 --> 00:04:38.778 position:50% align:center
He's a... Uhh...

00:04:38.862 --> 00:04:40.321 position:50% align:center
--[HANDA] ...a crab.
--[HINAICHI] A crab?

00:04:40.405 --> 00:04:41.740 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI]
That thing is obviously a bat!

00:04:41.823 --> 00:04:44.617 position:50% align:center
No! This is a species
of crab skilled at mimicry!

00:04:44.701 --> 00:04:46.536 position:50% align:center
What are you even
talking about Handa?

00:04:46.619 --> 00:04:48.329 position:50% align:center
There's no way that's a crab.

00:04:48.413 --> 00:04:50.373 position:50% align:center
Are you trying to
trick her or something?

00:04:50.457 --> 00:04:52.667 position:50% align:center
Do you take me
for a liar, Sagyo?!

00:04:52.751 --> 00:04:56.087 position:50% align:center
I'm not! My mother taught me
very well that lying is bad!

00:04:56.171 --> 00:04:58.548 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Wow, Handa.
You're a terrible liar.

00:04:58.631 --> 00:05:01.092 position:50% align:center
This is a crab! Its common
name is Bat-like Crab,

00:05:01.176 --> 00:05:02.510 position:50% align:center
normally found in
the Kanto region.

00:05:02.594 --> 00:05:03.970 position:50% align:center
It's technically
a type of hermit crab

00:05:04.054 --> 00:05:05.388 position:50% align:center
in the same family
as the coconut crab,

00:05:05.472 --> 00:05:06.598 position:50% align:center
but a crab nonetheless!

00:05:06.681 --> 00:05:08.224 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Doubled down!

00:05:08.308 --> 00:05:10.435 position:50% align:center
This lil' guy looks
too cute to be a crab.

00:05:10.518 --> 00:05:11.978 position:50% align:center
What are you, a crabologist?!

00:05:12.062 --> 00:05:13.980 position:50% align:center
Something wrong
with a cute little crab?

00:05:14.064 --> 00:05:15.982 position:50% align:center
[SAGYO] It's not a matter of
whether it's cute or not,

00:05:16.066 --> 00:05:17.317 position:50% align:center
it's just not a crab--

00:05:17.400 --> 00:05:19.361 position:50% align:center
[HANDA] If I say it's a crab,
then it's a crab!

00:05:19.444 --> 00:05:21.237 position:50% align:center
Look carefully!

00:05:21.321 --> 00:05:22.989 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
C-C-Crab!

00:05:23.073 --> 00:05:25.200 position:50% align:center
[SAGYO] Crabs don't
make sounds like that!

00:05:25.283 --> 00:05:27.619 position:50% align:center
I agree. I'm doing my best.

00:05:27.702 --> 00:05:29.621 position:50% align:center
They make whatever
sounds he makes!

00:05:29.704 --> 00:05:32.415 position:50% align:center
"Crab!" is the sound they
make in mating rituals.

00:05:32.499 --> 00:05:33.249 position:50% align:center
Uh?

00:05:33.333 --> 00:05:34.417 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Huh?

00:05:34.501 --> 00:05:35.710 position:50% align:center
--[HANDA grunts]
--[DRALUC] Eh?

00:05:35.794 --> 00:05:37.837 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC grunts]
C-Crab!

00:05:37.921 --> 00:05:41.383 position:50% align:center
A courtship display! I think
this guy really likes you.

00:05:41.466 --> 00:05:43.635 position:50% align:center
What in the world
am I doing this for?

00:05:43.718 --> 00:05:44.177 position:50% align:center
[HIYOSHI] Hey.

00:05:44.260 --> 00:05:44.719 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Sand!

00:05:44.803 --> 00:05:45.929 position:50% align:center
[GROUP yelps]

00:05:46.012 --> 00:05:47.597 position:50% align:center
[HIYOSHI] Has anyone
seen my fake mustache?

00:05:47.681 --> 00:05:49.516 position:50% align:center
[SAGYO] Please don't scare
us like that, Captain.

00:05:49.599 --> 00:05:51.810 position:50% align:center
How did you lose your
fake mustache this time?

00:05:51.893 --> 00:05:53.520 position:50% align:center
It doesn't look good
on you, you know.

00:05:53.603 --> 00:05:56.439 position:50% align:center
[HIYOSHI] I didn't ask.
What are you all doing, anyway?

00:05:56.523 --> 00:05:58.274 position:50% align:center
You really don't wanna know.

00:05:58.358 --> 00:05:59.693 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Sand...

00:05:59.776 --> 00:06:02.028 position:50% align:center
Okay, I swear I saw something
that looked like ashes!

00:06:02.112 --> 00:06:02.821 position:50% align:center
That must mean he's--

00:06:02.904 --> 00:06:04.572 position:50% align:center
You idiot! These are eggs!

00:06:04.656 --> 00:06:06.825 position:50% align:center
You made a move on it,
so it laid a bunch of eggs!

00:06:06.908 --> 00:06:08.368 position:50% align:center
You're a father now, so step up!

00:06:08.451 --> 00:06:10.203 position:50% align:center
[SAGYO] There's no way
I'd make a move on a crab!

00:06:10.286 --> 00:06:11.871 position:50% align:center
Come on! Anyway,
that's not a crab!

00:06:11.955 --> 00:06:13.707 position:50% align:center
[yelps, screams]

00:06:13.790 --> 00:06:16.584 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI] The crab turned into,
I dunno, something gross!

00:06:16.668 --> 00:06:18.378 position:50% align:center
Oh, my little Snort, why?

00:06:18.461 --> 00:06:20.714 position:50% align:center
Why did you give him
that terrible name?

00:06:20.797 --> 00:06:22.882 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI] Because of that sound
it was making.

00:06:22.966 --> 00:06:24.342 position:50% align:center
[HANDA chuckles]

00:06:24.426 --> 00:06:25.760 position:50% align:center
[cackles]

00:06:25.844 --> 00:06:27.804 position:50% align:center
You-- You foolish fools!

00:06:27.887 --> 00:06:29.514 position:50% align:center
It's a crab! Okay?!

00:06:29.597 --> 00:06:32.142 position:50% align:center
It's a... This is a crab larva!

00:06:32.225 --> 00:06:34.352 position:50% align:center
It must've hatched
from the eggs earlier!

00:06:34.436 --> 00:06:36.604 position:50% align:center
[SAGYO]
You know nothing about crabs!

00:06:36.688 --> 00:06:39.149 position:50% align:center
What about Snort?!
What happened to him?

00:06:39.232 --> 00:06:40.900 position:50% align:center
He, uh... Well, you see,

00:06:40.984 --> 00:06:42.944 position:50% align:center
during the, uh,
crab breeding cycle

00:06:43.028 --> 00:06:45.613 position:50% align:center
everything's passed to the
child, so the parents die!

00:06:45.697 --> 00:06:48.616 position:50% align:center
[SAGYO] You don't have any idea
what you're talking about!

00:06:48.700 --> 00:06:49.617 position:50% align:center
Ga-goo!

00:06:49.701 --> 00:06:50.785 position:50% align:center
[SAGYO]
Oh, just shut up!

00:06:50.869 --> 00:06:52.370 position:50% align:center
Don't talk to
your child that way!

00:06:52.454 --> 00:06:53.747 position:50% align:center
You're gonna mess up his head!

00:06:53.830 --> 00:06:54.998 position:50% align:center
Read a book or something!

00:06:55.081 --> 00:06:56.583 position:50% align:center
[SAGYO] You need to cut it with
this nonsense!

00:06:56.666 --> 00:06:58.335 position:50% align:center
Stop teasing me, dammit!

00:06:58.418 --> 00:07:01.004 position:50% align:center
He looks harmless, but he's a
vampire, isn't he?

00:07:01.087 --> 00:07:03.048 position:50% align:center
You really have to get
this guy checked out.

00:07:03.131 --> 00:07:04.299 position:50% align:center
[HIYOSHI]
Yeah!

00:07:04.382 --> 00:07:05.342 position:50% align:center
[SAGYO]
Uh!

00:07:05.425 --> 00:07:06.843 position:50% align:center
[HIYOSHI] 
I'll take care of it.

00:07:06.926 --> 00:07:09.471 position:50% align:center
[SAGYO] By the way,
did you find your moustache?

00:07:09.554 --> 00:07:11.514 position:50% align:center
[HIYOSHI]
Yeah.

00:07:11.598 --> 00:07:13.516 position:50% align:center
[SAGYO sighs]

00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:15.977 position:50% align:center
What was that whole
fiasco about, anyway?

00:07:16.061 --> 00:07:18.438 position:50% align:center
What were you so
desperate to hide?

00:07:18.521 --> 00:07:21.483 position:50% align:center
Whoa! Handa's about
to blow his top!

00:07:21.566 --> 00:07:23.985 position:50% align:center
I know you.
The vampire at Ronaldo's.

00:07:24.069 --> 00:07:25.445 position:50% align:center
Your name's Draluc, right?

00:07:25.528 --> 00:07:27.113 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Uh. Yes, that's me!

00:07:27.197 --> 00:07:28.573 position:50% align:center
I knew it.

00:07:28.656 --> 00:07:31.868 position:50% align:center
Why were you pretending to
be a crab looking like that?

00:07:31.951 --> 00:07:34.579 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
I'm curious. Tell me.

00:07:34.662 --> 00:07:37.248 position:50% align:center
How did you figure out
that I am Draluc?

00:07:37.332 --> 00:07:39.584 position:50% align:center
I know there's a strange
vampire at Ronaldo's

00:07:39.668 --> 00:07:40.794 position:50% align:center
who is bad at transforming,

00:07:40.877 --> 00:07:43.505 position:50% align:center
likes video games,
and dies in no time!

00:07:43.588 --> 00:07:46.758 position:50% align:center
Oh. I read about it
all in a book.

00:07:46.841 --> 00:07:49.260 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Hmm...

00:07:49.344 --> 00:07:51.763 position:50% align:center
Hey, Captain! I'll take Little
Snort after you're done--

00:07:51.846 --> 00:07:54.349 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Sand!

00:07:54.432 --> 00:07:55.767 position:50% align:center
[HIYOSHI, HINAICHI]
Hm?

00:07:56.976 --> 00:07:59.312 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC chuckles]
Crab.

00:08:02.607 --> 00:08:03.775 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Cod? Why?

00:08:03.858 --> 00:08:06.820 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC grunting]

00:08:06.903 --> 00:08:09.406 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC pants]
So much has happened.

00:08:09.489 --> 00:08:11.449 position:50% align:center
Oh, but first!
I have good news!

00:08:11.533 --> 00:08:13.535 position:50% align:center
I can turn into a bat now!

00:08:14.703 --> 00:08:16.496 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Check it out! See?

00:08:17.872 --> 00:08:20.000 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Here we go...

00:08:20.083 --> 00:08:21.876 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Hey, look.

00:08:21.960 --> 00:08:23.378 position:50% align:center
[JOHN grunts]

00:08:24.546 --> 00:08:27.507 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO sighs]
I need to take out the trash.

00:08:27.590 --> 00:08:29.300 position:50% align:center
It's been three days
since the first child

00:08:29.384 --> 00:08:31.261 position:50% align:center
went missing in
a series of kidnappings.

00:08:31.344 --> 00:08:32.887 position:50% align:center
And according to the police...

00:08:32.971 --> 00:08:34.305 position:50% align:center
Oh, I see.

00:08:34.389 --> 00:08:37.350 position:50% align:center
The kidnapper hasn't made
any demands for a ransom?

00:08:37.434 --> 00:08:38.643 position:50% align:center
Hm?

00:08:38.727 --> 00:08:40.395 position:50% align:center
[JOHN]
Nu...

00:08:40.478 --> 00:08:43.815 position:50% align:center
I agree; it's likely that
this is the work of a vampire.

00:08:43.898 --> 00:08:45.567 position:50% align:center
Yes, they should
bring in Vamp Control.

00:08:45.650 --> 00:08:47.402 position:50% align:center
Bye.

00:08:47.485 --> 00:08:49.237 position:50% align:center
Morning, John!

00:08:49.320 --> 00:08:50.572 position:50% align:center
[JOHN]
Nu!

00:08:50.655 --> 00:08:51.781 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Huh?

00:08:52.949 --> 00:08:55.201 position:50% align:center
You wanna go to the
local futsal tournament?

00:08:55.285 --> 00:08:56.453 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaks]

00:08:56.536 --> 00:08:58.997 position:50% align:center
Not sure. I'm worried
about you going alone.

00:08:59.080 --> 00:09:02.083 position:50% align:center
[JOHN]
Nu, nu. Nu!

00:09:02.167 --> 00:09:03.877 position:50% align:center
Uh. Hm...

00:09:05.462 --> 00:09:07.922 position:50% align:center
There, take that
personal alarm with you.

00:09:08.006 --> 00:09:10.008 position:50% align:center
If anything happens,
just pull the string.

00:09:10.091 --> 00:09:11.509 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaks]

00:09:11.593 --> 00:09:12.677 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
It's dangerous out there,

00:09:12.761 --> 00:09:14.262 position:50% align:center
so make sure
you're home by five.

00:09:14.346 --> 00:09:15.722 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaks]

00:09:19.809 --> 00:09:21.269 position:50% align:center
[JOHN]
Nu!

00:09:21.353 --> 00:09:23.480 position:50% align:center
[FUTSAL PEOPLE yell]

00:09:27.942 --> 00:09:28.985 position:50% align:center
[JOHN shouts]

00:09:29.069 --> 00:09:30.779 position:50% align:center
[FUTSAL PEOPLE yell]

00:09:30.862 --> 00:09:31.654 position:50% align:center
Go, John!

00:09:31.738 --> 00:09:32.781 position:50% align:center
Yeah, get 'em!

